- 8 collateral damage cards;
- 30 unit cards;
- 12 custom dice;
- 18 punchboard tokens (Start, Pass, Act);
- 12 punchboard funnel tokens;
- 12 punchboard effect tokens (Smoke, Final Move, Collateral Damage);
